s. blake, age 55, has been executive vice president business development and corporate operations since march2002. he was formerly the deputy secretary of energy
from may2001 until march2002. from june2000 until may2001, he was a senior vice president at general electric company and was vice president of ge power systems, from
february1996 until june2000. mr.blake also serves as a director of the southern company.
john
h. costello, age 57, has been executive vice president merchandising and marketing since august2003. he previously served as the company's executive vice
