september2001 until november2002. from september1999 until august2001, he was the chief executive officer of mvp.com. he was president of autonation,inc. from
december1998 until august1999 and senior executive vice president of sears from april1993 until december1998. mr.costello currently serves as a director of the
bombay company,inc.
